@node "ASLleft" "Left Edge"
@next "ASLtop"
@prev "Installation"
Value for the left edge of the ASL file requester.
@endnode

@node "ASLtop" "Top Edge"
@next "ASLwidth"
@prev "ASLleft"
Value for the top edge of the ASL file requester.
@endnode

@node "ASLwidth" "Width"
@next "ASLheight"
@prev "ASLtop"
Value for the width of the ASL file requester.
@endnode

@node "ASLheight" "Height"
@next "Installation"
@prev "ASLwidth"
Value for the height of the ASL file requester.
@endnode

@node "outputwin" "Output-Window"
The output window to open when decompressing an archive.  An example would
be:

@{i}CON:CON:0/14/600/300/UNPacker Version 2.0 Output/AUTO@{ui}
@endnode

@node "reqquester?" "Open Requester?"
@next "autoclose?"
@prev "Installation"
If an "all done" indicator requester is desired then enter N for NO.  Entering
Y for yes will pop up a requester indicating that UNPacker is all done.
@endnode

@node "autoclose?" "Auto Close Output Window?"
@next "Installation"
@prev "reqquester?"
If the output window is to be automatically closed upon completion then enter
N for no. Entering a Y for yes will close the output window as soon as the
uncompressing is done.
@endnode
